<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.7">
<l>maruṭṭār meṉkuḻal koṇṭu poḻilpukku</l>
<l rend="indent">vāyvaittav vāyartam pāṭi</l>
<l>curuṭṭār meṉkuḻal kaṉṉiyar vantuṉṉaic</l>
<l rend="Indent">cuṟṟum toḻaniṉṟa cōti</l>
<l>poruṭṭā yamilē ṉemperu māṉuṉṉaip</l>
<l rend="indent">peṟṟakuṟ ṟamallāl maṟṟiṅ</l>
<l>karaṭṭā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak</l>
<l rend="indent">kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Splendour who, entering the grove of that herder village</l>
<l rend="indent">with [your] soft flute full of enticement [and,]</l>
<l>placing [it] to [your] lips, stood while maidens with soft curls</l>
<l rend="indent">and coiled garlands came, surrounded and worshipped you!</l>
<l>Now I have no other fortune, my lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">but the misfortune of getting you.</l>
<l>Rascal! I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
